    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{\\widetilde{\\alpha_1}-\\alpha}{\\sqrt{D}}\\sqrt{n} \\; \\widetilde{\\longrightarrow} \\; N(0,1) \\\\\n",
    "{\\alpha_1}=M(\\xi)=\\int_{0}^{\\infty}xe^{-x}dx = -\\int_{0}^{\\infty}xde^{-x}=-xe^{-x}\\bigg|_0^\\infty + \\int_{0}^{\\infty}e^{-x}dx=0+1=1\\\\\n",
    "{\\alpha_2}=M(\\xi^2)=\\int_{0}^{\\infty}x^2e^{-x}dx = -\\int_{0}^{\\infty}x^2de^{-x}=-xe^{-x}\\bigg|_0^\\infty + \\int_{0}^{\\infty}e^{-x}dx^2=\\int_{0}^{\\infty}2xe^{-x}dx=2\\\\\n",
    "D={\\alpha_2} - {\\alpha_1}^2 = 2-1^2=1 =>\\\\\n",
    "\\widetilde{\\alpha_1}\\;\\widetilde{\\longrightarrow} \\; N(1,\\frac{1}{n})\\\\\n",
    "n=25\\\\\n",
    "D=0.04\\\\\n",
    "\\ \\sigma=\\sqrt{D} = 0.2\\\\\n",
    "\\mu = 1\\\\\n",
    "p(x)=\\frac{1}{\\sigma\\sqrt{2\\pi}}e^{\\frac{-(x-\\mu)^2}{2\\sigma^2}}\n",
    "$$"

    "$$\n",
    "P(t\\leq\\xi_k<t+dt,\\; v\\leq\\xi_l<v+dv) =\\\\\n",
    "nP(t\\leq\\xi_k<t+dt)*(n-1)P(v\\leq\\xi_l<v+dv)*C_{n-2}^{k-1}P^{k-1}(-\\infty\\leq\\xi_k<t)*C_{n-k-1}^{l-k-1}P^{l-k-1}(t+dt\\leq\\xi<v)*C_{n-l}^{n-l}P(\\xi_l\\geq v+dv)^{n-l}=>\\\\\n",
    "f(t_k,t_l)=\\frac{n!}{(k-1)!(l-k-1)!(n-l)!}p(t_k)*p(t_l)*F^{k-1}(t_k)*(F(t_l)-F(t_k))^{l-k-1}*(1-F^{n-l}(t_l))\\\\\n",
    "$$"
   ]
